        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-12 text-sm">
        Last updated: January 30, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose-legal space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
