          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Bask is a vitamin D and sun exposure tracking application designed for iOS. The App provides UV index data, personalized sun exposure recommendations, and vitamin D tracking tools. The App is intended for informational and wellness purposes only.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">3. Medical Disclaimer</h2>
