            Certain features of the App may require a paid subscription. Subscriptions are billed through Apple's App Store and are subject to Apple's terms and conditions. You may manage or cancel your subscription through your App Store account settings. Refunds are handled in accordance with Apple's refund policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
