        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            The App is provided on an "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" basis without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied. We do not warrant that the App will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components. We make no guarantees regarding the accuracy of UV data, sun exposure calculations, or vitamin D estimates.
